## Backend Persistence

When creating or modifying data services or persisted entities:
1. Check `.claude/standards-backend.md` for the collection registry
2. New entity types need: model → data service → `BACKUP_ENTITY_TYPES` entry → BackupService wiring
3. Plans MUST include `## Backend Impact` section

For full rules: `.claude/standards-backend.md`
